item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Policy_Acceptance
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Policy_Acceptance Datatype Description Represents the acceptance status of a Policy. Local acceptedFlag Flag to indicate if a policy has been previously accepted. Type: boolean policyName Name of the policy for which we are representing it's acceptance status. Type: string productPolicyAssignmentId ID of the [[SoftLayer_Product_Item_Policy_Assignment]]. Type: integer
